column3: “Tilray patient review here. This has to be my favourite daytime strain from Tilray. Although this strain is supposedly indica dominant the effects are more sativa like. A head clearing euphoria comes on quick which relieves my stress and anxiety. As the stress melts away the indica creeps in to provide mild to moderate pain relief. The high is uplifting and a little energizing, there is no sleepy couch lock effect. I...”

“Very satisfied, got the high CBD variant from the guys at Tilray, was tested at 11% THC and 11.4% CBD. Overall bud appearance was good, smell was fantastic with a more florally sweet and earthy sent which was very pleasantly. The high was minimal due to the low THC content but left the body in the state of euphoria without the couch constraints. bottom line, this strain would have to be one of my top pics at the mome...”
“I vape this high CBD strain most mornings. It eases my Crohns symptoms and keeps inflammation down. Great medicinal strain!”

“This was my first time trying out 2 grams of Warlock. At first I was skeptical because of the name but I still had a feeling i've heard of the name before and one of my friends said it seemed like a really good strain that people look for, but he wasn't positive either. Well, I gotta say he was right. What calmed me down at first was the look of it, boy did these buds look good. And from what I recall it had a very p...”

“Very  enjoyable. There was a slight giddiness accompanied by a relaxing body sensation. I went out to eat Mexican food and it tasted so damn good after having smoked this. A nice, relaxing and not overly powerful strain. Although it relaxes, it did not make me tired. Very agreeable.”
“Good beginners strain.”

“Incredible taste!, Lime, and pine it's very rare that i'll be able to taste this delectable aroma first trying this strain. Love both parents and this is the best of both worlds. The haze of the skunk with happiness and stonery haze and soft but heavy indica that is so pure! It's like a really great combo. 
The Look: Bud structure looks like phat lady fingers even the small buds are very long and thin towards the top...”
“Heady and inimate yet uplifting and optimisic with a common propensity to proclaim wow
column5: after ten minutes and up to an hour or two. The name fits this hermetic cave-dwelling indica, but once your inside the creative and philosophical juices flow leading to a stone that calms your mind and body but will uplift your soul and consiousness. Great for people with a heavy tolerance to Indicas and need anxiety...”

column3: “Lite green and purple nugs. Super frosty! Glistning with crystals. Sweet, pungent smell. Musky smoke with a slight fruity aftertaste. Made my nose itch. Warlock does pack a punch. Shit hits you hard! Kinda comes out of nowhere. Super strong high. I could feel my muscels start to loosen up midway through the joint. Left me feeling relaxed and even headed. Definitly a indica dominant hybrid. 30 minutes later i was all ...”

“Small pack gave me a strong body and head buzz. Really had me thinking and listening to music. Doesn't put you to sleep but relaxes you. Has a citrusy taste and is amazing in a blueberry blunt.  Highly recommend trying if able to pick it up. #allido”

“This is a very powerful strain for the seasoned smoker. I was really impresssed by how long this strain kept me high, which was around 4 - 5 hours off a 1g blunt. The reason i rated it an 8 out of 10 was because, although it kept me extremely medicated for an extended period of time, it just didnt have that special quality to the high that some of my favorite strains have. This was still an EXTREMELY IMPRESSIVE strai...”

“This is a great strain, love the smell, the smoke, the high. A great movie/game strain. Doesn't have a couch lock feeing & haven't had cotton mouth yet from smoking it. A day high that doesn't stop you from getting things done.”

“This is a great option for those looking for some mind and body relief but not a crazy high. I'm prone to get anxiety and this calms me right down. Great taste. I can still focus and get shit done when smoking this.”
“I smoked just 1 or 2 joints out of this weed, the effects lasted for about 3 hours! Really good stuff”
“This has your classic skunk flavor with the afghan twist. Great for task handling and leaves a happy cloud around you.. CannTrust 04-2016”
“Great strain for the day.”
“Warlock is a new fave, great for focusing and getting things done. The buds were packed with crystals. A relaxing high without a cloudy head.”

“A real classic smoke, which possesses both sativa and indica benefits, soothing the soul whilst sending you into a creative jam. A creative smoke that makes you want to skank to the afro beats in the background. No matter whats happened in the day, you can relax  late afternoon with this tasty treat. Bop out the beats, reduce frantic ruminations, and say goodbye to any physical discomfort.”

“Although it is a Indica-dom, its effects are very much that of a sativa.   Energetic, focused full body high that comes on quick. Great for cleaning or playing video games. One of my favourite strains for daytime use”
“This has your classic skunk flavor with the afghan twist. Great for task handling and leaves a happy cloud around you.. CannTrust 04-2016”

“got the cbd strain from tilray. fantastic anxiety and insomnia relief. strong berry smell along with a taste that, to me, resembles berry yogurt. busts up small due to stickyness, however it's a minimal issue.”

“As an African-American, Ordained Pagan Minister Warlock Lord, Sexual-Vampyre, Hedonist, Retired Marine Officer, when I discovered there was a weed strain named 'Warlock', well I just had to have it.  I traveled 30-minutes one-way just to obtain some.  It is an indica-dominant strain.  It does have a sweet and sour aroma.  The taste is skunky with no surprise having been crossed with Skunk and Afghani varieties.  Afte...”

“I vape a high CBD strain from Tilray and absolutely love it! It has a delicious fruity, cherry like aroma and flavour. I feel relaxed but not too high, and still focused and productive. Great for day use to curb anxiety.”

“I just received this strain for Tilray, the buds look and smell great. I broke up a little bit eager to test it and see how great it is for daytime smoking.  The initial head high came on fast but wasn't as intense as other strains.  There was a very euphoric feeling that overcame my body about an hour in and I could feel all my muscles relax and I was ready to go for a walk and enjoy the sun.  After a couple hours I...”

“I vape a high CBD strain from Tilray and absolutely love it! It has a delicious fruity, cherry like aroma and flavour. I feel relaxed but not too high, and still focused and productive. Great for day use to curb anxiety.”
“Super great for anxiety. Usually pretty good 1:1 ratio. Always pleased with this one.”

The taste is skunky with no surprise having been crossed with Skunk and Afghani varieties.  Afte...”
“Warlock should be called couchlock. its great if you like heavy hitting indicas”
“Felt a face buzz, small mind high but kind of weak for me.”
“Great strain, very useful for my treating my anxiety. Great tasting as well!”
“i liked it. smelled really nice and tasted good. the high was mostly located in my eyes and face and head, but gave me some body high effects too. i would purchase this strain again.”
“I got super high.”
“After smoking this I instantly became euphoric. A great strain to smoke if you're feeling down or are just looking to have some fun”

“(A top 5 strain in my opinion)
Good for hash too👍”

“One of the folks at a local dispensary suggested this and I'm happy they did. Good evening pre-bedtime with great taste and flavor. A little goes a long way. Indica leaning but not a knock out punch. At the end of the day it will help with the sweet dreams to come.”

“I had a variant called warlock CBD.
Excellent flavor, great body feeling, worked for medical reasons very well”

“This review is for the Warlock CBD

For the CBD lovers, this strain is for you. Very relax effects and clear headed. After a long day at work, it's the perfect mood for me. No side effects. I use it for relief stress and depression. Even if it has a light buzz"  because of the low THC
column4: the fact it relieves stress also help for insomnia. The smell was very sweet (candy sweet) and would definitely recommend to people ...”"

column3:
“almost 1:1 thc/cbd around 10%.
Puffin up a spliff of this truly special strain is pure bliss. entourage effect perhaps? Tilray produced this magic pain reliever for those of us who need it
A sweet and earthy taste and feelings of euphoria combine to make Warlock CBD just right !”
“good for low tolerance people or when you need a little bit of pain relief without getting too high.”
“This strain gives me crazy headaches, but it will leave you relaxed. I did not feel any CBD qualities. I have to smoke around 1g to feel sleepy. It is a nice smoke, but not my go-to flower.”

“I did not expect this strain to put me to sleep so quickly. If you're watching a movie that isn't super actiony with lots of explosions you will make it about 10 minutes through. 
That being said, beautiful earthy smell/taste and a warm fuzzy high that simply makes you grin from ear to ear. Absolutely recommend to those with trouble eating/sleeping or anyone with anxiety of any form.”
“I absolutely love Warlock for my chronic Fibromyalgia pain. I don't get the side effects that are listed either. Truely is an awesome strain!”
“Great Hybrid!”
“Excellent strain. Heavy at first, then a long lasting happy bake. Not the greatest in taste and look but the the overall punch and relief sure make up for it.”

“I love this strain (with the CBD variant) for how it totally takes my pain away, leaving me relaxed and happy but still able to focus and get shit done. The smell is yummy, and reminds me of rum and wine Colts. Sweet and fruity. The taste is not so good for me, sadly. It's harsh and I make faces on the exhale; it's just so gross to me. So only four stars because of the taste.”
“it made me feel very happy and social. it made me wanna hang out with all my friends all at once.”

“I purchased a high CBD phenotype of Warlock to try. I always like to try as many of the different high CBD strains as I can since those are best for treating Arthritis pain and generally leave you functional. This strain is okay, nothing too remarkable about it. It provided moderate pain relief, a relaxed feeling with very little in the way of a head high." The effects come on quickly after vaping but don't last all...”"
“The buds smell very sweet and unique with a hint of sage or something I assume this is what a wizard would smell like". I can't exactly get the taste down though.”"

“warlock has 2 genotype. Both are well obalelé but he has more quality indica buds and more branches. Usually matures between 55-60 day. While sativní genotype needs more time, but it has a huge main head, but often very thin and light after drying.”

“Earthy taste is right, like smoking dirt out of a stick. high is pretty mellow and not overpowering. mostly in the head, but a little body tingle to go with it. probably won't buy again based on the flavor”
“gave me a major headache”
“This is a good beginner strain. It wasn't a heavy high because the high cbd.”
“very earthy like smell. it had a very smooth hit the smoke wasnt harsh. the nug looked brownish. very crystaly”
“weak indica, probably good for someone that wants to smoke/vape a bunch of bud...”

“Warlock +CBD actually

OMG that was brutal. This stuff gets you high AF. Me 'n my boyfriend tried it today, and he had more because I'm always so careful to ease into this for fear of anxiety/paranoia. It was worse than any anxious/paranoid feeling. I barely had any, and we're new to this medicinal stuff but used to smoke weed when we were teens. This was like..trippy. Very racy. I laughed a few times about something...”
